This is just a project to study about THREEjs

Business:
- I just want to use THREE to visualize own Solar
- The center is Sun, it will rotate be ifself
- All planets of Solar will rotate around the Sun and rotate by itself also
- Build some planet's ring, planet's satellite

To run app:
- Open your terminal and go to project
- Run command `npm start`
- See on your terminal, app will run on a local server with URL display on terminal
- Click or copy this URL and paste to your browser